{title [Index]}
{css-src common.css, ucs cfr, global []}
{global, orbit heading, h2 []}
'Standard index units: index, heading, equation, figure, theorem units'
[]
'The compiled result of an index unit consists of four parts: tag, mark, desc and content. Tag part is from the orbit. Mark part is from non-empty mark option or the index. Desc part is from desc option. Content part is from the children.'
[]
{h2 [Index Tag Unit]}
'We call a general index unit an index unit. In contrast, we call a unit whose tag is exactly "index" an index tag unit.'
[]
Index tag units are most basic index units.
[]
Adding "plain" class can hide tag part which is a common feature of all index units and many other built-in units.
[]
{two [
    {display [Source]}
    {display [Result]}
    {lang stdn, code [
        '{align ['
        '    [\'H_0(pt)&=\tilde H_0(pt)\oplus\Z \tag*{\'{id h-vs-h-tilde, orbit equation, index []}\'}\'\\\]'
        '    [\'&=\Z \tag*{\'{orbit equation, mark {['
        '        [{ref-id h-vs-h-tilde, class plain, ref []}{\'\\\'\'}]'
        '    ]}, index []}\'}\']'
        ']}'
    ]}
    {align [
        ['H_0(pt)&=\tilde H_0(pt)\oplus\Z \tag*{'{id h-vs-h-tilde, orbit equation, index []}'}'\\]
        ['&=\Z \tag*{'{orbit equation, mark {[
            //
            [{ref-id h-vs-h-tilde, class plain, ref []}{'\''}]
        ]}, index []}'}']
    ]}
]}
[]
{hr []}
[]
Index tag units are compiled in inline mode by default which can be changed by "block" option.
[]
{two [
    {display [Source]}
    {display [Result]}
    {lang stdn, code [
        '{orbit article, block, index ['
        '    [\'M. F. Atiyah and R. Bott, \'{i [The moment map and equivariant cohomology]}\', Topology 23 (1984), no 1, 1-28.\']'
        ']}'
    ]}
    {orbit article, block, index [
        //
        ['M. F. Atiyah and R. Bott, '{i [The moment map and equivariant cohomology]}', Topology 23 (1984), no 1, 1-28.']
    ]}
]}
[]
{h2 [Heading Tag Unit]}
Tag part of a heading tag unit is hided.
[]
{two [
    {display [Source]}
    {display [Result]}
    {lang stdn, block, code ['{heading [Test]}']}
    {heading [Test]}
    {lang stdn, block, code ['{level 2, heading [Test]}']}
    {level 2, heading [Test]}
]}
[]
